le/Therapeutic bathing|13=User:Immanuelle/Thermal bath|qq=|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1004887}}, {{ill|Therapeutic hot spring resort|ja|湯治場|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Therapeutic hot spring resort|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 湯治|1=thermal bath|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1004887}} * {{ill|Hidden hot spring|ja|隠し湯|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hidden hot spring|qq=}}, [[:en:Shugendō|Shugendō]] * {{ill|Difficult-to-access areas|ja|交通困難地|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Difficult-to-access areas|qq=|1=Difficult-to-Access Area|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11373988}} – many Hitō are designated as such * {{ill|Japan Secret Hot Springs Preservation Association|ja|日本秘湯を守る会|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japan Secret Hot Springs Preservation Association|qq=|1=Japan Association of Secluded Hot Spring Inns|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11508755}}
